A sleek minimalist composition showing a single elegant interface wireframe floating in pristine white space, rendered as a delicate blueprint-style illustration with thin precise lines in IBM blue. The wireframe depicts an abstract web layout with clean geometric sections - header, sidebar, content areas - all perfectly aligned in a harmonious grid structure. Subtle shadows give the flat design gentle depth. Small geometric shapes in complementary colors (teal, soft gray) orbit around the main wireframe like design elements being organized. The overall feeling is of sophisticated digital craftsmanship and systematic design thinking, evoking the careful attention to detail that goes into building consistent user interface frameworks.
